text: San Giuliano Terme is a comune (municipality) in the Province of Pisa in the Italian region Tuscany. It is about west of Florence and about northeast of Pisa. == Notable people == Nazario Pardini (1937), essayst and poet ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website * Health and Nature in Tuscany Category:Towns in the Province of Pisa Category:Province of Pisa
